{"tid":23952,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（新手上路）想試下買股票","createTime":"2016-12-05T09:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T19:10:02.000Z","uid":51200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cfaa550460a74dd65ddddc5e6966a3e33bcee752","tid":23952,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:10:01.000Z","msg":"暫時有兩個問題想請教巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一，小弟係學生，只係想嘗試下學投資，<br />\n賺蝕無問題，只用pt零用錢，起始資金需要幾多左右？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，小弟用恒生個人戶口，<br />\n大家認為需唔需要揾過另一間銀行／證券行開股票戶口呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，上網見到有人話恒生既戶口收費同交易費較高，不利新手，可唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29352d560fc7cfd668fc61bc854d08dd9fbf9c8","tid":23952,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時有兩個問題想請教巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一，小弟係學生，只係想嘗試下學投資，<br />\n賺蝕無問題，只用pt零用錢，起始資金需要幾多左右？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，小弟用恒生個人戶口，<br />\n大家認為需唔需要揾過另一間銀行／證券行開股票戶口呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，上網見到有人話恒生既戶口收費同交易費較高，不利新手，可唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 豐儉由人，你鐘意做一手達人玩藍籌又得，玩細價股又得，玩下國指/細期/牛熊又得<br />\n但你話賺蝕都冇問題咁同你入賭場比娛樂費有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n2. 佣金越低成本就越低，X通收你5蚊但銀行收你一舊水，咁你明差別啦？<br />\n<br />\n但證劵行比銀行有較高倒閉風險<br />\n不過政府投資者賠償基金包底15萬，本細就唔洗怕"},{"pid":"c5ad7445d4b3d600cf8048b27f7bdc496df44713","tid":23952,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暫時有兩個問題想請教巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一，小弟係學生，只係想嘗試下學投資，<br />\n賺蝕無問題，只用pt零用錢，起始資金需要幾多左右？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，小弟用恒生個人戶口，<br />\n大家認為需唔需要揾過另一間銀行／證券行開股票戶口呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，上網見到有人話恒生既戶口收費同交易費較高，不利新手，可唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 豐儉由人，你鐘意做一手達人玩藍籌又得，玩細價股又得，玩下國指/細期/牛熊又得<br />\n但你話賺蝕都冇問題咁同你入賭場比娛樂費有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n2. 佣金越低成本就越低，X通收你5蚊但銀行收你一舊水，咁你明差別啦？<br />\n<br />\n但證劵行比銀行有較高倒閉風險<br />\n不過政府投資者賠償基金包底15萬，本細就唔洗怕</blockquote><br />\n先多謝巴打回覆，其實我今次最主要只係想摸熟個流程，睇下自己岩唔岩玩，<br />\n唔會掉太多，所以先話志不在賺錢，<br />\n不過當然執到少少就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5,6000至10000做唔做到本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於開戶我要做多少少功課先，順便儲多少少本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def65cecb0d70c11643d169b0d9c887eb99a269c","tid":23952,"uid":20707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"留名學野<br />\n岩岩開左個股票戶口<br />\n諗住專心買一隻睇下點先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660aa57350cf011ad668e3eb71c845c12c418b8f","tid":23952,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>暫時有兩個問題想請教巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一，小弟係學生，只係想嘗試下學投資，<br />\n賺蝕無問題，只用pt零用錢，起始資金需要幾多左右？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，小弟用恒生個人戶口，<br />\n大家認為需唔需要揾過另一間銀行／證券行開股票戶口呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外，上網見到有人話恒生既戶口收費同交易費較高，不利新手，可唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 豐儉由人，你鐘意做一手達人玩藍籌又得，玩細價股又得，玩下國指/細期/牛熊又得<br />\n但你話賺蝕都冇問題咁同你入賭場比娛樂費有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n2. 佣金越低成本就越低，X通收你5蚊但銀行收你一舊水，咁你明差別啦？<br />\n<br />\n但證劵行比銀行有較高倒閉風險<br />\n不過政府投資者賠償基金包底15萬，本細就唔洗怕</blockquote><br />\n先多謝巴打回覆，其實我今次最主要只係想摸熟個流程，睇下自己岩唔岩玩，<br />\n唔會掉太多，所以先話志不在賺錢，<br />\n不過當然執到少少就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5,6000至10000做唔做到本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於開戶我要做多少少功課先，順便儲多少少本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n10000蚊 買兩手內銀放係到由佢擺咪算"},{"pid":"fd7d9b0aca8fde8f9f73fdbcdb68c66b82ae108d","tid":23952,"uid":29212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"是旦買隻一兩手都蝕唔死人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f89554ee38a706838c1f8fb6afcd4bc9d0cea8f","tid":23952,"uid":12467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩出黎做野有50k本玩下"},{"pid":"dc1451d3f7a8b94ac2936de8cc2e5bec1174453c","tid":23952,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n對股票一竅不通 唔知點入手好"},{"pid":"215eb668da41348b230cb7a980bb3035c9c05fee","tid":23952,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislik