img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f30b2055cb45f0995a1a1f54ebc1510a992826","tid":23952,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:23:21.000Z","msg":"建議睇書學<br />\n聽講《股票投資101》哩本唔錯"},{"pid":"f5216277aa7d1c034f59d0d13bdd306d1b6567d8","tid":23952,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我決定做多幾個月功課先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n查資料見到有好多唔明既terms之餘 , <br />\n亦都要對比下唔同既證券行／銀行既收費，<br />\n仲有查清楚唔同既股票玩法同衡量多少少風險，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外又想儲到16-20k先入市，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似襟玩d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f47f5762244351ffd4d605c5d64cd4268227ffc","tid":23952,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝咁多位解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我決定做多幾個月功課先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n查資料見到有好多唔明既terms之餘 , <br />\n亦都要對比下唔同既證券行／銀行既收費，<br />\n仲有查清楚唔同既股票玩法同衡量多少少風險，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外又想儲到16-20k先入市，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似襟玩d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反正唔急於－時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac6232c6a8ec9d3073acc1e31b6e8b7ca42bbb4","tid":23952,"uid":20943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beaaa5f287b6ad8399caa41708dc187558eb991c","tid":23952,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"Lau ming learn stuff"},{"pid":"b8454f1037f9c45affcb3a8cded46aecae18a7f9","tid":23952,"uid":56607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:10:15.000Z","msg":"我都係學生，我用intern同自己本身嘅錢玩  因為懶同其他原因用main bank開服票戶口 每筆買賣總計大概2百幾手續費，但頭半年免買入手續費，回番百幾蚊<br />\n因為宜家手續費至少都百幾，所以我通常每次交易買大概20000蚊左右嘅藍籌，執1千幾百左右就放<br />\n分析主要都係睇下圖表數據，留意下新聞咁樣<br />\n<br />\n利申短線投機者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5163d4308e38a40a905dda6b0f506e04c96ad1f6","tid":23952,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買手700 包你日日貼住個市 一個月學識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買你好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買你好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f5abc36a89bf28d8e3d05da6f0e11b380678ba","tid":23952,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:07:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買手700 包你日日貼住個市 一個月學識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買你好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買你好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好買我<br />\n垃圾石油股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a255c853d39f6b604ac32c26f55a9342860611","tid":23952,"uid":45369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:11:44.000Z","msg":"初學 忌買8字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bca3bfb73292b3f2285227270660c62eceb421","tid":239